<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/pics/favicon2.png  " type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gasoek+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
 body{
    background-color: #726fa9;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content:center;
    height: 100vh;
    align-items: center;
    gap:1rem;
    font-size: 16px;
 }

 .errorMessage{
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-family: 'Gasoek One', sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    color: #d1ff4f;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
 }
.messageText{
    color:#46fad1;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;

}

 .returnButton{
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#46fad1,#57b48a);
    color:#19504a;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 2px 3px 10px #000;
 }

 .returnButton:hover{
    transform: scale(0.92);
    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    color:#07291a;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#57b48a,#46fad1);
 }
</style>

</head>
<body class="errorContainer">
    <img src="/pics/white-logo-ocw.png" alt="">
    <h1 class="errorMessage">Error 404</h1>
    <p class="messageText">No encontramos la página que intentabas buscar, pero puedes regresar a nuestra página principal haciendo click en el botón aquí abajo.</p>
    <a class="returnButton" href="/">Volver a la pagina principal</a>
</body>
</html>